                    "company": "EcoValue",
                    "description": "Under the name EcoValue (consultancy founded in 2006), I support clients from various sectors.\n\nMy vision is of a circular economy, in which we use natural resources smarter, in cyclical ways. Natural and social capital are taken into account. True prices include \u2018externalities\u2019, taxes shift from human to natural resources (including pricing carbon). Allowing the natural system to replenish its gold: fresh water, clean air, nutrient-rich soils, carbon-capturing forests, natural areas rich in biodiversity, healthy fisheries. I see it as my job to illustrate why, and show how this can be done. \n\nI continue my focus on the financial and agribusiness sectors, where I am mindful of the need to \u2018translate between sectors\u2019. Different professions can speak very different languages. Think of traders who need to make large volume decisions in split seconds, speaking to NGO\u2019s who want the trader to take into account multiple variables. Or policy makers who look at what is possible, working with scientists who look at what is needed.\n\nI enjoy building bridges, working in multidisciplinary teams towards a shared goal. Do contact me if I can be of assistance to your organization, or if you want to explore new ideas.\n\nRead more on my website: www.ecovalue.nl",
                    "title": "Senior Sustainability Advisor",
                    "employment_type": null
                }
            ]
